name: 10-25976-oy4v-xk37
notes: The study objective was to test the effectiveness of proposed best management practices used in wetland road crossings to maintain the natural hydrological regime of boreal wetlands. Study locations included various sites in the Duck and Porcupine Mountains in Manitoba and the Pasquia Hills in Saskatchewan. Water quality samples were taken at all sites as part of this project.

notes_translated.en: The study objective was to test the effectiveness of proposed best management practices used in wetland road crossings to maintain the natural hydrological regime of boreal wetlands. Study locations included various sites in the Duck and Porcupine Mountains in Manitoba and the Pasquia Hills in Saskatchewan. Water quality samples were taken at all sites as part of this project.
notes_translated.fr: L'objectif de l'étude était de tester l'efficacité des meilleures pratiques de gestion proposées pour les franchissements routiers des zones humides afin de maintenir le régime hydrologique naturel des zones humides boréales. Les sites d'étude comprenaient divers sites dans les montagnes Duck et Porcupine au Manitoba et dans les collines Pasquia en Saskatchewan. Des échantillons de qualité de l'eau ont été prélevés sur tous les sites dans le cadre de ce projet.
